# Python Environment
- Always use existing .venv in workspace root
- Never create new virtual environments
- Activate with: source .venv/bin/activate

# ETL Pipeline
- Run from workspace root with venv activated
- Config: etl/config/dev.yaml
- PDF extractor: pymupdf (fast), not unstructured (slow)
- Requirements: etl/requirements.txt

# Project Structure
- Rust code: crates/ and apps/
- Python ETL: etl/
- Data: dev_data/raw (PDFs) -> dev_data/txt (processed)
- Models: models/bge-m3/

# Common Commands
- ETL: cd etl && python load.py --env dev
- Rust build: cargo build
- Search: scripts/run_search.sh
